        }
      ],
      "text": "<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Aptos,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Calibri&quot;,sans-serif\">A microbiology resident is comparing the growth patterns of a bacterial culture under two different conditions: on a standard growth medium and in an enrichment medium. She notices distinct differences in the bacterial growth curves under these two conditions. Which of the following best describes the difference in bacterial growth in an enrichment medium compared to a standard growth medium?</span></span></span></span></p>",
